We are seeking an Advisor (Program Controls & Reporting) to join our team
based in Brisbane.

** Requirements of the role **   
• Previous experience working in a Program or Project Controls environment.  
• Effective communication skills in presenting technical information in a
userfriendly manner, fostering collaboration and shared understanding.  
• Experience in independently analysing data and proactively address
challenges through effective problem-solving and presenting will considered
solutions.  
• Advanced level skills in Microsoft Excel

To apply, please provide the following information to assess your suitability:  
\- A cover letter (maximum two pages)  
\- Your CV (maximum four pages). Ensure that you outline your key achievement
and experience and demonstrate how you meet the requirements of the role.

Applications will remain current for 12 months.

